New-patches: lord@regexps.com--2002/package-framework--lord--1.0--patch-12


`PLUGIN/options': added `configure' option:

		configure --with sendmail PROG

	for help in locating the sendmail program, if it is 
	to be used to implement a `mailx'-style mail sending
	program.

`install-shell-subcommands.mk': added support for installing `awk' 
				helper scripts.

`cpp-to-includes.sed': tweaked the script for greater portability.

